    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0002",
      "text": " 104",
      "bbox": [
        518.28,
        723.59,
        537.71,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0003",
      "text": "LS_ACC: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        142.05,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0004",
      "text": "LS_ACC signifies acceptance of the SRL Request.  If the period scanning is enabled then",
      "bbox": [
        142.08,
        57.65,
        540.01,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0005",
      "text": "the switch shall return the value of the periodic scanning period in the LS_ACC payloads Scan Period",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        69.65,
        539.98,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0006",
      "text": "field, If the periodic scanning period is disabled then the switch shall set the LS_ACC payload Scan",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        539.97,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0007",
      "text": "Period field to zero. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        93.65,
        184.93,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0008",
      "text": "4.2.40",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        202.96,
        123.77,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0009",
      "text": "Set Bit-error Reporting Parameters (SBRP)",
      "bbox": [
        133.77,
        202.96,
        336.42,
        214.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0010",
      "text": "4.2.40.1  Description",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        226.96,
        192.63,
        238.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0011",
      "text": "Set SBRP ELS is used to communicate a set of bit error reporting parameters to a Port or to all Ports",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        250.96,
        539.83,
        262.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0012",
      "text": "in a particular Domain in a Fabric.  There are 3 parameters, Error Interval, Error Window, and Error",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        262.96,
        540.02,
        274.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0013",
      "text": "Threshold.  Error Interval is the time period over which bit error bursts are integrated to produce a sin-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        274.96,
        539.95,
        286.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0014",
      "text": "gle reported error.  An Error Window is composed of one or more Error Intervals.  The Error Interval",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        286.96,
        540.0,
        298.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0015",
      "text": "Count is the number of Error Intervals occurring in an Error Window.  If the Error Interval Count is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        298.96,
        540.0,
        310.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0016",
      "text": "greater than or equal to the Error Thrshold, a Registered Link Incident Report (RLIR) is generated",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        539.95,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0017",
      "text": "with an Incident Code specifying Bit-error-rate threshold exceeded (see FC-FS-2).  At the end of the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        322.96,
        540.03,
        334.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0018",
      "text": "Error Window, the count is set to zero and the process is repeated.  See figure 2 for illustration of the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        334.96,
        539.89,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0019",
      "text": "parameters.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        346.96,
        149.27,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 9,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0020",
      "text": " Figure 2 – Illustration of parameters",
      "bbox": [
        231.6,
        538.96,
        404.37,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0021",
      "text": "SBRP may be used to determine an acceptable set or the current set of bit error reporting parame-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        539.94,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0022",
      "text": "ters in the destination Port or Domain, without changing the settings. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        574.96,
        401.0,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0023",
      "text": "The setting of parameters in a particular Port or Domain is done by a controlling entity that is outside",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        540.03,
        610.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p123_s0024",
      "text": "the scope of this standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        213.13,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
